{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1561890/extras/RR_logo_steam_desc.png?t=1728478927\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1561890/extras/is_a_kaleidoscopic_first_person.png?t=1728478927\" />Manipulate an infinitely recursive landscape to solve a series of environmental puzzles as you work through your own struggles with grief and a creative crisis. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With Behemoth, The Cat at your side \u2014 or at least somewhere nearby \u2014 unlock an introspective journey through your past and discover new meaning in a chaotic world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1561890/extras/Behemoth_w_Border.gif?t=1728478927\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>A Dying, Visually Stunning World</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Lose yourself in the Infinite Realms, a dying, fractal world of strange beauty and mind-bending physics that repeats eternally inward and outward. Uncover the secrets of seven hypnotizing landscapes filled with hidden spaces and bizarre celestial denizens. Overcome the impossible and use circular logic to manipulate recursive physics and solve challenging, self-referential puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1561890/extras/LandscapeKaleidoscope_w_Border.gif?t=1728478927\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>A Deeply Personal Journey</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Begin an introspective search for meaning and experience a bittersweet story that cascades into the surreal. Use your unique abilities and shape the world to beat back the scourge known as Ichor, a malevolent substance eating away at the fabric of reality.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1561890/extras/ArtistTakingWorkHome_w_Border.gif?t=1728478927\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Rediscover Meaning, and Hope</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Through the fight against the Ichor, and the satisfying completion of peculiar puzzles, balance out the chaos of the Infinite Realms and reconcile your own inner turmoil. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1561890/extras/Violin_w_Border.gif?t=1728478927\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Recursive Ruin","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1561890/87cc8492e9af29b47da8652c75463685db2b356e.jpg"},{"name":"Strange Aeons, I","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1561890/527b0ec20a92de7f1bea4eb86cdbdff1372d7445.jpg"},{"name":"The Citadel which sits at Eternity","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1561890/8148a7ee1e1792e98911af4286d3a30a97621b9f.jpg"},{"name":"Strange Aeons, II","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1561890/04251e243109c4861b6a6dd2e04747f04305a47c.jpg"},{"name":"Echoes which ring Eternal","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1561890/f7d0a2213f6bc949a62577e987dcef1ae1b74259.jpg"},{"name":"???","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1561890/ad7bc1a5c4fb91eb1bec12c03790f04ba960da28.jpg"},{"name":"Spires Ascending into Forgotten Forevers","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1561890/d3a7dee11d8ff136487086119dd30893bcde4b97.jpg"},{"name":"Strange Aeons, III","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/ste